content.text:
The following communication was laid before the Senate, together with 
accompanying papers, reports, and documents, and was referred as 
indicated:

        EC-3444. A communication from the Secretary of the Senate, 
     transmitting, pursuant to law, the report of the receipts and 
     expenditures of the Senate for the period from April 1, 2017 
     through September 30, 2017, received in the Office of the 
     President of the Senate on November 14, 2017; ordered to lie 
     on the table.
